Medical Records Manager

Overall goal of this project is to provide interface for patients and doctors to be able manage medical records and history of visits as well as being able to generate reports

Main entities are doctors, patients and visit records includes doctor notes, diagnosises and medications as well as metrics taken during the visit - height, wieght and blood pressure

Project implemented as a group of microservices with common interface and registration:

1. Patient Service with below API *:
  - browsing patients information and medical history
  - update patients information

2. Doctor Services with below API *:
   - browsing patients information and medical history
   - update patients information and medical history

* A level of doctor/patient isolaton is guranteed that patients and doctors will only be able to browse and edit information relevant to them

